  <h2>At the Post Office</h2>

  <p>Take the following to any
   <a href="http://www.postoffice.co.uk/branch-finder">Post Office</a>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>completed V11 reminder</li>
    <li>insurance certificate or cover note</li>
    <li>MOT test certificate if required (must be valid when the tax disc starts)</li>
    <li>the payment shown on the reminder</li>
  </ul>

